  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/825620/extras/e610c19b2e5e86bbef3ccd10b4f4a913.avif?t=1537256501\" width=450 height=100 /></span><br><br>M.I.N.D. Is a retro-style platformer about, and set in a malfunctioning mind control device.<br><br>The game is story-focused, with new and innovative one or two-player gameplay. The game's short length is made up with greatly varied bits of different gameplay, including puzzles, platforming and a space shooter.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/825620/extras/4b2daeaeb3f9ba4a46221e1c5509290a.avif?t=1537256501\" width=450 height=100 /></span><br><br>M.I.N.D. Is made with Clickteam Fusion by two Finnish 15-year-olds, Kasper and Johannes. We're only trying to cover the developement costs of this projects with the release, so you're supporting us and our future careers by buying this game!",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/825620/extras/e610c19b2e5e86bbef3ccd10b4f4a913.avif?t=1537256501\" width=450 height=100 /></span><br><br>M.I.N.D. Is a retro-style platformer about, and set in a malfunctioning mind control device.<br><br>The game is story-focused, with new and innovative one or two-player gameplay. The game's short length is made up with greatly varied bits of different gameplay, including puzzles, platforming and a space shooter.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/825620/extras/4b2daeaeb3f9ba4a46221e1c5509290a.avif?t=1537256501\" width=450 height=100 /></span><br><br>M.I.N.D. Is made with Clickteam Fusion by two Finnish 15-year-olds, Kasper and Johannes. We're only trying to cover the developement costs of this projects with the release, so you're supporting us and our future careers by buying this game!",
